                                                                <span style="font-size: 15px;"><span data-custom-class="body_text">However, please note that this will not affect the lawfulness of the processing before its withdrawal nor, when applicable law allows, will it affect the processing of your personal information conducted in reliance on lawful processing grounds other than consent.</span></span>
