                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                    <div style="line-height: 1.5;">
                                                                                      <span style="font-size: 15px;"><span data-custom-class="body_text">We may request that you provide additional information reasonably necessary to verify you and your consumer's request. If you submit the request through an authorized agent, we may need to collect additional information to verify your identity before processing your request.</span></span>
                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                    <div style="line-height: 1.5;">
                                                                                      <br>
                                                                                    </div>
                                                                                    <div style="line-height: 1.5;">
                                                                                      <span style="font-size: 15px;"><span data-custom-class="body_text">Upon receiving your request, we will respond without undue delay, but in all cases, within forty-five (45) days of receipt. The response period may be extended once by forty-five (45) additional days when reasonably necessary. We will inform you of any such extension within the initial 45-day response period, together with the reason for the extension.</span></span>
